but if my brother was here,
we could've voted this thing through.

07:00.186 --> 07:04.384
What's this?
A stuffy office meeting?

07:04.490 --> 07:08.984
Well, maybe it's time
for a little... <i>Office Magic.</i>

07:09.095 --> 07:14.431
- What's "office magic"?
<i>- Sometimes it's as simple as turning 10:45...</i>

07:14.534 --> 07:18.470
in the morning into lunchtime!

07:18.571 --> 07:21.836
- Okay.
- Why does lunch have to be so dull?

07:21.941 --> 07:26.139
Maybe you'd
prefer some chicken instead!

07:26.245 --> 07:29.806
All right. Let's cut.
Take five, everybody.

07:29.916 --> 07:33.147
- No, no. We're not takin' five.
Hey, is this guy with you?
- Yeah, he's an actor.

07:33.252 --> 07:36.278
Well, you know, I thought
he was an investor. He voted against me...

07:36.389 --> 07:38.949
which is the vote I asked you
to be here for, so-

07:39.058 --> 07:42.858
