I don't think I can work with you anymore.

07:42.962 --> 07:45.453
- You kind of have to, guy. I'm the president.
- No. I'm the president.

07:45.565 --> 07:49.399
No. You lost the presidency, just like you did
in high school when you refused to play dirty.

07:49.502 --> 07:51.970
- Worked when I ran.
- We're talkin' about the office here, okay?

07:52.071 --> 07:54.062
I do all the work. I've been helping you.
That's over now.

07:54.173 --> 07:58.007
Sorry to hear you say that, Michael,
'cause it just cost you your job.

07:58.110 --> 08:00.874
- I'm serious. It's over.
- How do you call Security on this thing?

08:00.980 --> 08:04.040
- You hit pound-zero-zero to operate the system.
