08:06.953 --> 08:09.387
- Hit pound and then zero-zero.
- I do. I know.

08:09.489 --> 08:12.390
Tell you what. You don't need to learn
the system, because you're out of here.

08:12.492 --> 08:14.983
You're fired.

08:15.094 --> 08:16.994
Have Security send a man up.

08:17.096 --> 08:19.496
You've got the wrong guy.

08:19.599 --> 08:22.591
<i>Uh, no, you don't,</i>
<i>but you don't have to do this.</i>

08:22.702 --> 08:26.433
<i>But the guard had recently</i>
<i>lost halfhis tie to</i> Office Magic.

