- Oh, I don't mind.
- Get this. You getting this?

08:29.509 --> 08:32.409
Cheat out.
You have to cheat out a little bit.

08:32.511 --> 08:35.174
- Oh, hey.
- What was that all about?

08:35.280 --> 08:38.114
Your uncle doesn't
not-work here anymore.

08:38.217 --> 08:42.517
- So I guess your mom told you
