08:44.957 --> 08:48.017
- Neither of them do.
- Sorry. Guess I shouldn't have said anything.

08:48.127 --> 08:51.290
Maybe I should just start
keeping some secrets of my own.

08:51.397 --> 08:53.456
Why aren't you at school right now?

08:53.566 --> 08:56.057
Marry me.

08:56.168 --> 08:59.069
I'm so sorry.
I forgot who I was talking to.

08:59.171 --> 09:02.766
I was just using your copier
to make some campaign posters.

09:02.875 --> 09:05.639
Well, then, by all means,
let me help you out.

09:05.745 --> 09:08.543
I mean, I don't even know why I'm doing it.
He's gonna win by a landslide.

09:08.648 --> 09:11.139
- That's what I was tellin' him.
- How do you know Steve Holt?

09:11.250 --> 09:13.650
